Better Homes and Garden Real Estate Paracle

data.description:
Here's your chance to own an easy-care townhome in the heart of Antiquity & Old Town Cornelius! This 2 story brick home features BRAND NEW luxury vinyl plank flooring, a kitchen & breakfast bar w/ granite countertops, 42"cabinetry, modern stainless & black appliances. Upstairs are two primary bedrooms, each with its own private ensuite & walk-in closets! Courtyard/terrace is fully privacy-fenced & leads to your one car garage (big enough for current owner's SUV). HOA includes exterior maintenance of building as well as front lawn maintenance & pruning.
Prime location in walking/biking distance to restaurants, entertainment & shopping. Antiquity boasts its own covered bridge, community pool, open-air clubhouse, nature trails & dog park. Prime location allows you to walk/bike to restaurants, shops, the Cain Center for The Arts - and is close to amenities in Old Town Cornelius and downtown Davidson. Antiquity is also next to miles of Greenway Trails! A MUST SEE!
